==Eat== * {{eat | name=Cafe Kadijk | alt= | url=http://cafekadijk.nl/ | email=info@cafekadijk.nl | address=Kadijksplein 5 | lat=52.37012 | long=4.91210 | directions=Bus 22 and 48 to Kadijksplein | phone=+31 61 774 4411 | tollfree= | hours= | price=Main dishes range between €17 and €22 | lastedit=2020-10-30 | content=Cafe Kadijk is a small Indonesian restaurant that offers good food at a decent price. The restaurant has a coffee shop vibe and is located in a "trendy" area. Just outside Amsterdam's city centre, it is a bit of a walk away from the more touristy areas of the city. Patio dining and indoor dining are both available. }} * {{eat | name=De plantage | alt=Café-Restaurant de Plantage | url=https://caferestaurantdeplantage.nl/en/#home | email=info@caferestaurantdeplantage.nl | address=Plantage Kerklaan 36 | lat=52.36677 | long=4.91241 | directions=Tram 14 to Artis | phone=+31 20 760 6800 | tollfree= | hours=M-F 09:00-01:00, Sa Su 10:00-01:00 | price=Approx € 25 for main course | lastedit=2025-06-22 | content=Big restaurant with a nice terrace in the summer, open all day with breakfast, lunch and dinner. }} * {{eat | name=Restaurant Plancius | alt= | url=https://planciusgroot.nl/ | email=info@planciusgroot.nl | address=Plantage Kerklaan 61 | lat=52.36785 | long=4.91277 | directions=Tram 14 to Artis | phone=+31 20 223 6946 | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2020-10-30 | content=Has a nice high tea. }} * {{eat | name=Tempura | alt= | url=https://www.restauranttempura.nl/ | email=tempura1018@gmail.com | address=Plantage Kerklaan 26 | lat=52.36599 | long=4.91159 | directions=Tram 14 to Artis | phone=+31 20 4287132 | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2020-10-30 | content=Nice Japanese restaurant, with a very lovely guest woman. }} * {{eat | name=De Pizzabakkers | alt= | url=https://www.depizzabakkers.nl/ | email=plantage@depizzabakkers.nl | address=Plantage Kerklaan 2 | lat=52.36553 | long=4.91117 | directions=Tram 14 to Artis | phone=+31 20 625 0740 | tollfree= | hours=Su-Th 12:00-21:00, F 12:00-22:00 | price= | lastedit=2020-10-30 | content=Hip pizza restaurant, with good stone-baked pizzas. Suitable for children. Almost always busy, so reservation is recommended. }} * {{eat | name=Aguada | alt= | url= | email= | address=Roeterstraat 10HS | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price=€ 18 for mains as at 2025 | lastedit=2025-06-22 | content=Indian and Indonesian influenced. Cosy restaurant. The rendang is a little too sweet but the thali is excellent. }}
==Drink== *{{drink | name=Brouwerij 't IJ | alt= | url=http://www.brouwerijhetij.nl/?lang=en | email=info@brouwerijhetij.nl | address=Funenkade 7 | lat=52.36672 | long=4.92635 | directions=Tram 14 to Pontanusstraat, or tram 7 to Hoogte Kadijk | phone=+31 20 261 9801 | tollfree= | hours=W-Su 15:00-20:00 | price= | lastedit=2020-10-30 | content=Its label with an ostrich egg is a visual pun, as IJ and 'ei' - the word for egg - sound the same in Dutch. East of the centre, close to Artis Zoo, in a former bath house beside a windmill. A small-scale brewery where delicious beer in several varieties and strengths is brewed and sold - at a bar - on the premises. The beer is available at some specialist beer shops, and is of high quality and, in some cases, alcohol content. Internationally renowned! }} * {{drink | name=Café Smit & Voogt | alt= | url=https://www.cafesmitenvoogt.nl/ | email= | address=Plantage Parklaan 10 | lat=52.36736 | long=4.90955 | directions= | phone=+31 20 737 0829 | tollfree= | hours= | price= | image=Pml1.jpg | lastedit=2025-06-22 | content=Locals love this place. It is situated inside a beautiful building and has timber booths and seating inside . There is also seating on the footpath which is well placed to catch the afternoon sun. Serves a selection of beers and other alcoholic drinks and also serves food. You can usually get a seat for a drink but better to come early or book for food. Very friendly service. }}
