ess=De Boelelaan 2 | lat=52.335261 | long=4.888549 | directions=near the RAI conference centre, 15 minutes by tram #4 from city centre | phone=+31 20 646 2300 | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2016-07-30 | content=Ticks all the main boxes for facilities but about due for a refurbishment. }} * {{sleep | name=Park Plaza | alt= | url=https://www.radissonhotels.com/en-us/brand/park-plaza | email=bookamsterdam@pphe.com | address=Koninginneweg 34-36 | lat=52.354286 | long=4.866425 | directions=down the block from Vondelpark | phone=+31 20 664 61 11 | tollfree= | fax=+31 20 573 7130 | checkin= | checkout= | price=from €69-120 | content=Free Wi-Fi in public areas. }}
