|52.3823,4.8805 |52.3843,4.8818 |52.3883,4.8847 |52.3882,4.8858 |52.3885,4.8912 |52.3888,4.8957}} {{Mapshapes|Q2060132|stroke-width=2.5}} {{Mapshapes|Q260870}} === By train === The line between ''Amsterdam Centraal'', Amsterdam's main train station in the heart of its [[Amsterdam/Binnenstad|city centre]], and [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol]] runs through the middle of Amsterdam-West. There are two stations on that line - '''Amsterdam Lelylaan''' and '''Amsterdam Sloterdijk'''. Sloterdijk is a major interchange, situated on a railway crossing between the north-south line (serving all of [[North Holland]] north of Amsterdam and connecting to [[South Holland]] via Schiphol) and the east-west line between Amsterdam and [[Haarlem]]. Sloterdijk is served by both Intercity and Sprinter services, Lelylaan is served by Sprinter services only.
=== By metro === Metro lines '''50''' and '''51''' both pass westbound through Amsterdam Zuid station then turn northbound through the West district, terminating at Isolatorweg. Line '''50''' comes via [[Amsterdam/Zuid|Zuid]] from [[Amsterdam/Zuidoost|Zuidoost]] while line '''51''' comes via Zuid from Amsterdam Centraal Station in the [[Amsterdam/Binnenstad|city centre]]. Several metro stations with tram connections are: Heemstedestraat, Lelylaan, Jan van Galenstraat, Burgemeester de Vlugtlaan and Sloterdijk.
[[File:AmsterdamTram.svg|thumbnail|right|Amsterdam tram & metro system]]
=== By tram === These are the tram lines serving the West district as of January 2020: * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|1}} | alt=Muiderspoortstation to Osdorp de Akker | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/1 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=Passes westbound through Leidseplein and Vondelbuurt as it passes to metro station Lelylaan and terminates at Osdorp de Akker. }} * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|2}} | alt=Amsterdam Centraal to Nieuw Sloten | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/2 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=runs from Amsterdam Centraal via Leidseplein towards Rijksmuseum, passes Vondelpark on the southern side, passes metro station Heemsteedestraat and terminates at Nieuw Sloten in the south-west. }} * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|5}} | alt=Westergasfabriek to Amstelveen Stadshart | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/5 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=passes Leidseplein traveling north to Van Halsstraat (Westergasfabrik) near Westerpark which has an old gas plant (''gasfabrik'') converted into a cultural centre. Note: Until November 2022, Westergasfabrik is temporarily served by tram '''3''' from Marnixplein instead of line 5. }} * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|7}} | alt=Slotermeer to Azartplein | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/7 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=runs westbound through Leidseplein with a zig-zag route via Marnixstraat, west on Elandsgracht and Kinkerstraat, north on Hoofdweg, west passing Burgemeester de Vlugtlaan metro station and south on Slotermeerlaan to terminate at Sloterpark (Slotermeer). }} * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|13}} | alt=Amsterdam Centraal to Geuzenveld | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/13 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=runs from Amsterdam Centraal through Jordaan and northern Oud-West, then stops at the north end of Rembrandtpark, metro station Jan van Galen-Straat and terminates in Geuzenveld. }} * {{go | name=Tram {{rint|amsterdam|17}} | alt=Amsterdam Centraal to Osdorp Dijkgraafplein | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/17 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=runs from Amsterdam Centraal through Jordaan, but traverses Oud West further south than '''Tram''' {{rint|amsterdam|13}} and partly overlaps the route of '''Tram''' {{rint|amsterdam|1}}. It passes Lelylaan metro station to terminate at Osdorp Dijkgraafplein. }} * {{go | name=Tram 19 | alt=Diemen Sniep to Sloterdijk | url=https://reisinfo.gvb.nl/en/lijnen/19 | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | hours= | price= | lastedit=2023-11-21 | content=Passes through Leidseplein on a roughly northwest route to terminate at metro station Sloterdijk. }}
=== '''By bus''' === * Bus '''18''' runs regularly from Slotervaart via Mercatorplein, de Markthallen, Frederik hendrikbuurt and Haarlemmerplein to Amsterdam Centraal station * Bus '''21''' runs regularly from Geuzenveld via Slotermeer, Bos en Lommerplein, Staatsliedenbuurt, (the beautiful) Frederik hendrikplantsoen and Haarlemmer Houttuinen to Amsterdam Centraal station [[File:Dog statue.JPG|thumbnail|right|Dog statue in Rembrandpark]]
